55:30.920 --> 55:33.520
Great, see you. Bryan, Nigel?

55:33.800 --> 55:36.680
I'm just about to move
in for the big destroy.

55:37.080 --> 55:38.160
Oh, yeah?

55:56.960 --> 55:58.840
Hey... it's starting to rain!

55:59.960 --> 56:01.320
We'll get saturated!

56:01.440 --> 56:02.720
Let's head for that tree over there.

56:03.120 --> 56:04.080
Come on!

56:05.680 --> 56:08.080
It beats drowning. It's great, isn't it?

56:08.160 --> 56:09.240
Yeah, it's great!

56:11.960 --> 56:13.440
